    "updated_at": "2015-04-23T22:10:06Z",
    "body": "It does support Windows now when using [Squirrel for Windows](https://github.com/Squirrel/Squirrel.Windows/), you can generate an installer for your app that will automatically update using https://github.com/atom/grunt-electron-installer\n\nThe docs do need to be updated and there are still plans to adds more APIs for the auto-updater module for windows things such as desktop/start menu shortcuts, etc via https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/939\n"
